The Evolving Profile of Idiosyncratic Drug Induced liver Injury.
LiverTox is a comprehensive, freely accessible website with important information regarding the hepatotoxicity profile of over 1000 approved medications and 60 HDS products. Ongoing "omics" studies will hopefully lead to additional insight into DILI pathogenesis, improved diagnostic and prognostic biomarkers and mechanism-based treatments.
